{"tid":1753484,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"下一步拉埋藍絲一齊屌林奠","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T17:15:52.000Z","uid":80972,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a6293a858836e0062558bebebbfe35deedf2bd0","tid":1753484,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"區議會有壓倒勝嘅民意，林奠必須回應五大訴求。我諗係無腦淺藍絲都明白嘅野。<br />\n<br />\n林奠咁仆街，可能會拎1,2個訴求出黎拖下。到時拉埋d淺藍絲出黎一齊屌鳩林奠，因為大家都會明白呢個係解決反送中問題<span style=\"color: red;\">唯一答案</span>及<span style=\"color: orange;\">最佳時機</span>。<br />\n<br />\n林奠再唔回應就後果自負。到時d淺藍絲都connect 埋，升級左就更少人割席。<br />\n<br />\n深藍絲就送返佢地去大灣區算"},{"pid":"f13efe11ed7223454129a93cce93e48fa3053ed6","tid":1753484,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c40d9377c936c85f71d01d1cc63e5eaac662913d","tid":1753484,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:05:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"10f23bb9fe4a803df4b139b61565ca516dc3dca5","tid":1753484,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51e026cad1b1e48fdfb66c9dbc711ef980cda58d","tid":1753484,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:05:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d52e51ee1ab0f6c918276a18ccdf87da9d32c538","tid":1753484,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:05:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a3b145034a45853a809cf5b115aaa463fe7abe94","tid":1753484,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f48d1b27a31c42650ec1349f98f10de595da052a","tid":1753484,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:06:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"68d2c4d26018e35e04c3b1a55789fadd7e197115","tid":1753484,"uid":132729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:07:13.0